everything you do, they were all yellow...

today is our 4 months.

i have loved him for 4 months.

it has been the best 4 months of my life.

i hope there's many more to come.

he made me cry happy tears for the first time in my life last night.

i love him more than anything or anyone in the world.

he is perfect...

it has been a perfect 4 months together.

happy 4 months baby, i love you.

3 months of love....

3  months.

hoy es tres meses.

tres.

three.

a long time.

3  months and i couldn't be happier...

hoy es nuestros 3  meses.

i just fucking love it...

"Beating Heart Baby" - Head Automatica

download it. do it now.

being lazy...don't wanna go straighten my hair...or put on make up...or get dressed...or anything. i dunno. bleh. but i need to.
i heard the song "under pressure" by the used and my chemical romance. i like the queen version better. jose told me about that song like a month ago. yup.
speaking of jose, things with him are a little...i dunno. like, i wanna tell him something, but i can't so i'm not and its bugging me so i'm like..ahh i dunno. he called me this morning to wake me up so i could get up and get ready and stuff...but i don't wanna get ready. he said he'd try to call me later...i hope he does, but i doubt he will.
so like...tonights gonna suck. i have nothing planned and it sucks. whatever though. i'll lay on my couch and watch...oceans eleven and jackass and the incredibles. yup..i'm that cool.
i want the weird guys to walk by again so i can make friends with them. maybe we could become friends and i could hang out with them...hmm. chris kinda scared one of them the other day...that kid was just a victiiiiim.
well i should go start getting ready to go thrift store shopping. i have $7 and then $5.75 in quarters...haha. yah well, i dunno, jeff and i needed cigarettes last night (he had 2 bucks) and i wanted a mcflurry. so...everyone was happy in the end.
last night was fun. i just hung out with jeff and andrea. when i got home, i talked to alex...then jose called. then nick called. then i called alex again and i was on the phone with her until like 2:30. i miss those nights...but shes back now. so yah..
ima go get ready. later.

It's amazing how you can speak right to my heart
Without saying a word, you can light up the dark
Try as I may I could never explain
What I hear when you don't say a thing.
The smile on your face lets me know that you need me
There's a truth in your eyes saying you'll never leave me
The touch of your hand says you'll catch me if ever I fall
You say it best, When you say nothing at all.


(country...yuuup.)
jose es el amor de mi vida...

heck yes i'm goin thrift store shopping tomorrow with larissa cuz i'm BROKE. yay!

i hung out with alex today...it was fun. we walked to starbucks, paid with quarters and a starbucks card... then went to chipotle and got chips...cuz they have the best chips EVER. we played darts too. and chilled in the garage, porch, and backyard. but then her boyfriend came and picked her up...yup.

jose didn't call me today... :( but, i called him around 5:30ish. so it was good just to hear his voice, even though it was for like only 5 minutes (at the most). i hope i hear from him soon...but i doubt i will. i'm so glad i have him and he understands me. but, both alex and i didn't get a call from our guys...kinda sad.

my computer broke so we had to reformat the whole hard drive (or something like that) so i lost ALL my pictures and my songs and...everything...i was sad. but, my computer is working again and that is all that matters. i'll post some pics from today up as soon as i can (probably tomorrow).

well i'm out. later yo.

te amo, jose.

why is it that everyone i get close to end up leaving me? that's how it always go for me...i feel like i don't have anyone anymore.

another thing, everyone always makes all of these promises to me, but...they always break them. i swear, i do not know a single person who has made a promise didn't break it. i don't know what it is...ricky does it, alan does it, alex does it, erica does it, my family does it...everyone i care about does it.

i'm starting to give up on everyone and everything...except him, not yet. i can't give up on him just yet.

I shouldn't say

i took this quiz and yah...this is what came up

    Your Existing Situation

      Persistent. Demands what she feels to be her due and endeavors to maintain her position intact.

    Your Stress Sources

      The existing situation is disagreeable. Has an unsatisfied need to ally herself with others whose standards are as high as her own, and to stand out from the rank and file. Her control of her sensual instincts restricts her ability to give herself, but the resulting isolation leads to the urge to surrender and allow herself to merge with another. This disturbs her. as such instincts are regarded as weaknesses to be overcome; she feels that only by continued self-restraint can she hope to maintain her attitude of individual superiority. Wants to be loved or admired for herself alone; needs attention, recognition, and the esteem of others.

    Your Restrained Characteristics

      Remains emotionally unattached even when involved in a close relationship.

      Becomes distressed when her needs or desires are misunderstood and feels that she has no one to turn to or rely on. Egocentric and therefore quick to take offense.


    Your Desired Objective

      Tries to escape from her problems, difficulties, and tensions by abrupt, headstrong, and ill-considered decisions. Desperately seeking a way to escape, and there is danger of reckless behavior to the point of self-destruction.

    Your Actual Problem

      The need for esteem--for the chance to play some outstanding part and make a name for herself--has become imperative. She reacts by insisting on being the center of attention, and refuses to play an impersonal or minor role.

    Your Actual Problem #2

      The fear that she might be prevented from achieving the things she wants drives her to the exploitation of all types of experience, so that she may categorically deny that any of them has any value. This destructive denigration becomes her method of concealing hopelessness and a profound sense of futility.

well yesterday was quite interesting. kyle calls me asks me if i wanna go to the mall so i say yes. kyle calls back and says courtney is goin too. ok. so then kyle calls back again and says adjmal wants to go to palm springs and go to the outlet mall with his friend. ok. so we drive to palm springs and go shoping. it was fun. we got there at like 3:15. i got 2 shirts. i'm surprised i found anything i like cuz all they had was preppy clothes and surf brands. i got a billabong shirt (i know, shocking) but its cool. you can barely tell its billabong. and i also got a brown BAM shirt. of course i had to get that. we went to starbucks there too and i got lemonade and when we were waiting for courtney and kyle's drinks, some guy made the wrong drink for a guy so the guy who worked there was like "WHO WANTS A FREE CARMEL FRAP?" and courtney, of course, was like "RIGHT HERE!!" and she was all excited cuz then she had 2 drinks. shes so funny. but then we left at about 6. went to BJs for pizza at 8. then went across the street to that place to get the dollar ice cream. it was all really good. then at about 10 i got home. so it was fun. on the way to palm springs, adjmal was driving crazy. it was funny, everyone was scared and shit...but i'm used to it cuz of jeff. but yah, i had fun. i got home and felt sick so i attempted to sleep. thats about it. it was fun. but yah i'm gonna go now...late

well yesterday wasn't the best. i had to go to that park opening thing for my dad. it was more like i stood there for 15 minutes looking around to see who was there. i saw liz. we made eye contact. i looked away. i saw a really hot greaser looking guy there. jeff made fun of him, so i didn't talk to him. but we did exchange glances. after they were done introuducing my dad, jeff and i left. we bought cigarettes then went to taco bell. on the way to taco bell, some black guy who was like 19 pulled up next to us. i looked over and he looked at me and smiled so i kinda smiled back. next thing i knew, he was trying to stay at the same speed as us. when we went into the left turn lane, he got into the lane next to it. i was like whoa. wtf? then we went to the drive though. we sat there and then i see his car drive by looking around the parking lot. so creepy. so we come home and eat. i sat around for awhile. walked to the library with jessica so she could get her book. some guy working there was semi-hot. why would hot people work at a library? stupid. then i came back. at about 5 wendy calls and asks if i can babysit for dane and tanner. so i go to her house and shes at her neighbors party. i take dane and tanner to the park. after a while, dane has to use the bathroom so i wait for him outside. all of a sudden this black guy walks past me and hes like staring at me and i noticed that he looked familiar so i'm like whatever and i don't make eye contact or anything. then he starts to walk into the bathroom, then he walks out and he stares at me and i give him a look like "what the hell do you want?" and hes like "do i know you from somewhere?" and i'm like "i dunno" then he asks what middle school i went to so i told him and he asks my name, so i told him. then hes like "oh i remember you. i'm quante" i'm like OMG! i didn't like him too much in middle school. then dane came out and quante was gone and then quante kept kinda walkin over to wherever i was. it was weird. so i go back and i watch the kids for a lil. we watch TV and stuff. then i somehow end up watching 5 kids? don't know how that happened. then i ended up with dane and his friend ben. we watched brother bear. cute movie. it was cool though. they were all really good. the 5 kids were tanner, megan, katie, dane, and ben. it kinda sucked...but i don't care. i got $50. i left a lil bit before 10. so thats pretty good. i came home and ate and then jeff wanted more cigarettes so i gave him some money then we went to carl's jr. and i got a shake and we came back and watched road trip. good stuff. thats it. i don't know what i'm gonna do today. i want to go to venice and get some more piercings, but i'll have to see if jeff will take me. yup...thats it. i'm out. late

soo yah this is about my trip to palm springs. i smoked like a whole pack of cigarettes. i decided to stop smoking. haha yah...random. well i have to admit that palm springs wasn't bad. i was wrong, i actally had fun. lemme break it down...

ride there- well first we went to breakfast, twas interesting. then we hit the road. boring. took us two hours. to kill time, john decided to play a game. called the "Car Race." object: look at a car that is kinda far away from you, guess what race the person driving it is. (i know, kinda racist, but it was john's idea.) however, if you guess the person's gender you get an extra point, and if you guess their age (old, young, middle age) you get another point. so you have a chance of getting 3 points per car. john won. my mom got 2nd. i got 3rd. jeff got 4th...yah. it was fun. oh yah, we drove through gardena...hottest guys ever.

hotel- not as hot as i expected. nice hotel. huge pool. golf course, it was cool. went to the room. i watched spongbob till it was over.

john's house- we get there. nothing really happens for awhile. after awhile i go swimming with andy, john's lil bro. hes so cute! then, i hung out with danielle. shes cool. i give ya the story on her later. then, jonathon came over. acted like an ass. we got pissed at him, but he threw a box of cigarettes at us. so we were happy. my parents leave. i stay. hang out in the hot tub with john's mom (shes so cool. she acts like shes my age. she lets us smoke, drink, whatever. shes cool), john's sister sandy, and his step-sister daniell. then we want to get jonathon back for being an ass. so, her mom makes us fake vomit to throw on his car. it looked so nasty. excatly like vomit. so we drive to the gas station (me, sandy, and danielle). they are like closed and we just wanted gas and a lighter. but we were like standing there and this really hot guy was standing there too and he had a lighter, made us happy. and like his hot asshole friend was like "you guys goin to a party?" and we're liek "no" and hes like "well then why'd you steel mommy's car?" and sandy is like "thats my car" and hes like "yah, right. i bet you only have your permit" and shes like "IM 20!"  asshole. he didnt believe us, so when we were drivin away, daniell was yellin things at him and givin him the finger and shit. it was so funny. then...we start following jeff, john and jonathon. they see us, we keep following them, realize we cant do the prank to them. go back to the house cuz jonathon went home. walk to jonathon's house. get attacked by a dog. drive to this guy brians house (only sandy and i) and throw the vomit on his car. looked real. i was like leaning out the window. good times. then...we went back. i slept in john's room on his futon. it was really fun. i like his family. gary is cool too...oh yah, john's mom kept telling me i was beautiful and stuff. it was funny. maybe shes BLIND?

the morning- woke up in the morning at like 8 cuz it was too hot to sleep. i got 4 hours of sleep. call my mom. she comes to pick up me and jeff and john. i get in the shower. jeff and john do whatever. then we go to del taco for breakfast. good shit. then go back to the hotel. drop john off...head for the freeway.
